    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved. It looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line, with a flawless exterior, a pristine interior that still smells new, and a mechanical system that operates with absolute precision. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a collector-grade vehicle with zero imperfections or maintenance needs.",
